OL,3,CPlans for 85 new homes near cinema
OL,4,Cunanimously approved
OL,6,FA major housing development next to
OL,7,FGuernsey's Mallard Cinema has been
OL,8,Funanimously approved, despite concerns
OL,9,Faround increased traffic and pressure
OL,10,Fon nearby services.
OL,12,FThe Mallard site in the Forest will be
OL,13,Fmade up of 85 designated affordable
OL,14,Fhousing units, including 34 homes and
OL,15,F51 flats, after it was granted outline
OL,16,Fpermission by the Development and
OL,17,FPlanning Authority (DPA) in an open
OL,18,Fmeeting.
