OL,6,FHowever, before any building work can
OL,7,Fbegin, a detailed planning application
OL,8,Fwill need further public consultation
OL,9,Fand final approval by the DPA.
OL,11,FPaul Nobes, Managing Director at the
OL,12,Fdevelopers Infinity Construction,
OL,13,Fexplains: "This development will
OL,14,Fprovide real hope for local families
OL,15,Fwho currently have limited choices.
OL,16,FOur team is ready to deliver these
OL,17,Fhomes as quickly as possible."
