OL,6,FAs part of the approval, conditions
OL,7,Fwere added to ensure the homes have
OL,8,Fsolar panels, a section of trees are
OL,9,Fprotected, and that the developer must
OL,10,Fconsult with environmental groups on
OL,11,Fnative planting schemes.
OL,13,FThe President of the DPA, Deputy Neil
OL,14,FInder, states: "The developer says he
OL,15,Fis going to be moving some of his
OL,16,Fother work and his resources straight
OL,17,Finto that site, so he is very keen.
