OL,6,F"The fact of the matter is that we
OL,7,Fneed more affordable housing. No
OL,8,Fapplication is going to be without its
OL,9,Fdrawbacks, so we have to be pragmatic.
OL,11,F"We can only deal with what we have
OL,12,Fgot in front of us, and if they don't
OL,13,Fmake the terms, then that planning
OL,14,Fapplication will be withdrawn."
