OL,6,FAndrew Merrett, Director of Lovell
OL,7,FOzanne Architects that designed the
OL,8,Fplans, adds: "The Mallard development
OL,9,Frepresents one of the most meaningful
OL,10,Fcontributions to Guernsey's housing
OL,11,Flandscape in a generation, and we are
OL,12,Fproud to help deliver it."
OL,14,FThose behind the development hope to
OL,15,Fstart building work in early 2026, if
OL,16,Fdetailed plans are given final
OL,17,Fapproval.
